        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="143" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>In the previous section, describing the concept of assigning posting dates, the intention of the Adjust Cost – Item entries batch job is to create a Value Entry with Posting Date September 10th.</source>
