        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="147" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>The user in this case has an allowed posting date range from September 11th to September 30th and is thereby not allowed to post the Adjustment Value Entry with Posting Date September 10th.</source>
