        <trans-unit id="194" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source><bpt id="p1">**</bpt>Review of Posting Dates on created Adjustment Value Entries:<ept id="p1">**</ept> The earliest allowed Posting Date the Adjust Cost - Item Entries batch job has to relate to is January 1st, 2014 as stated in the General Ledger Setup.</source>
